items.badge_description: Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 45 distinct venues!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 220 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 45!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 160 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 33!

Everyone loves fresh beer, but obviously not as much as you do. You went straight to the source. 

That's a beer at 15 different venues categorized as a Brewery, Cidery or Meadery. Visit 5 more for Level 4!
